{"type":"message","id":"4747c094","parentId":"922f1f7f","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:18:33.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户要查询数据库中最新的一条双色球开奖记录。我需要连接到SQLite数据库并查询最新的记录。\n\n数据库位置: `/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball/data/lottery_records.db`\n\n我应该使用 sqlite3 命令查询最新的开奖记录，按照期号倒序排列，取第一条。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-4251d5c31abf429da665f25207f8a4f9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && sqlite3 data/lottery_records.db \"SELECT issue_number, draw_date, red_ball_1, red_ball_2, red_ball_3, red_ball_4, red_ball_5, red_ball_6, blue_ball FROM lottery_records ORDER BY issue_number DESC LIMIT 1;\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":7923,"output":149,"cacheRead":37504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45576,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778750303990,"responseId":"20260514171824586c8110effd4bb3","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
