{"type":"message","id":"959f8018","parentId":"91b0a78b","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:24:25.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户询问大乐透技能是否能获取历史全部开奖数据存储到数据库中。目前只获取了几十条。\n\n让我检查一下 fetch_history.py 的实现，看看它是否有获取全部历史数据的功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8683f891e9024f629f17123ea8186a00","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":678,"output":66,"cacheRead":49792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50536,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778750660920,"responseId":"20260514172421b363e525467b4be5","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b177577","parentId":"959f8018","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:24:25.792Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-8683f891e9024f629f17123ea8186a00","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n大乐透历史数据爬虫脚本（简化版）\n使用requests + BeautifulSoup抓取彩票500万网站数据\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3\nimport requests\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\n# 数据库路径\nDB_PATH = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"data\" / \"super_lotto.db\"\n\n# 数据源配置\nBASE_URL = \"https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\"\n\n# 请求头\nHEADERS = {\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n    'Accept': 'text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/webp,*/*;q=0.8',\n    'Accept-Language': 'zh-CN,zh;q=0.9,en;q=0.8',\n}\n\n\ndef parse_html(html_content):\n    \"\"\"解析HTML内容，提取开奖数据\"\"\"\n    records = []\n    soup = BeautifulSoup(html_content, 'html.parser')\n    \n    # 查找表格中的所有行\n    rows = soup.find_all('tbody')\n    \n    for tbody in rows:\n        trs = tbody.find_all('tr')\n        for tr in trs:\n            try:\n                tds = tr.find_all('td')\n                if len(tds) < 15:  # 数据行应该有足够的列\n                    continue\n                \n                # 提取数据\n                issue_number = tds[0].get_text(strip=True)\n                \n                # 检查是否是有效的期号（数字）\n                if not issue_number.isdigit():\n                    continue\n                \n                # 前区（红球）- 5个号码\n                front_balls = []\n                for i in range(1, 6):\n                    ball = int(tds[i].get_text(strip=True))\n                    front_balls.append(ball)\n                \n                # 后区（蓝球）- 2个号码\n                back_balls = []\n                for i in range(6, 8):\n                    ball = int(tds[i].get_text(strip=True))\n                    back_balls.append(ball)\n                \n                # 开奖日期\n                draw_date_str = tds[-1].get_text(strip=True)\n                draw_date = datetime.strptime(draw_date_str, '%Y-%m-%d').date()\n                \n                # 奖池金额和销售金额（可选）\n                pool_amount_str = tds[8].get_text(strip=True).replace(',', '')\n                sales_amount_str = tds[13].get_text(strip=True).replace(',', '')\n                \n                try:\n                    pool_amount = int(pool_amount_str) if pool_amount_str else None\n                    sales_amount = int(sales_amount_str) if sales_amount_str else None\n                except:\n                    pool_amount = None\n                    sales_amount = None\n                \n                records.append({\n                    'issue_number': issue_number,\n                    'draw_date': draw_date,\n                    'front_balls': front_balls,\n                    'back_balls': back_balls,\n                    'pool_amount': pool_amount,\n                    'sales_amount': sales_amount\n                })\n                \n            except Exception as e:\n                # 忽略解析错误的行\n                continue\n    \n    return records\n\n\ndef fetch_all_history():\n    \"\"\"抓取全部历史数据\"\"\"\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    \n    all_records = []\n    \n    try:\n        print(f\"\\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\")\n        print(f\"   URL: {BASE_URL}\")\n        \n        response = requests.get(BASE_URL, headers=HEADERS, timeout=30)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        \n        print(\"📊 正在解析数据...\")\n        records = parse_html(response.content)\n        \n        if records:\n            all_records.extend(records)\n            print(f\"✅ 成功抓取 {len(records)} 条记录\")\n        else:\n            print(\"❌ 未抓取到数据\")\n        \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ 抓取失败: {e}\")\n    \n    # 保存到数据库\n    if all_records:\n        saved = save_to_database(all_records)\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 总计保存 {saved} 条记录\")\n        return saved\n    \n    return 0\n\n\ndef save_to_database(records):\n    \"\"\"保存数据到数据库\"\"\"\n    if not records:\n        print(\"⚠️ 没有数据需要保存\")\n        return 0\n    \n    if not DB_PATH.exists():\n        print(\"❌ 数据库文件不存在，请先运行 init_db.py\")\n        return 0\n    \n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    inserted = 0\n    updated = 0\n    \n    for record in records:\n        try:\n            # 检查是否已存在\n            cursor.execute(\n                'SELECT id FROM lottery_records WHERE issue_number = ?',\n                (record['issue_number'],)\n            )\n            \n            if cursor.fetchone():\n                # 更新已有记录\n                cursor.execute('''\n                    UPDATE lottery_records SET\n                        draw_date = ?,\n                        front_ball_1 = ?,\n                        front_ball_2 = ?,\n                        front_ball_3 = ?,\n                        front_ball_4 = ?,\n                        front_ball_5 = ?,\n                        back_ball_1 = ?,\n                        back_ball_2 = ?,\n                        pool_amount = ?,\n                        sales_amount = ?,\n                        updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n                    WHERE issue_number = ?\n                ''', (\n                    record['draw_date'],\n                    record['front_balls'][0],\n                    record['front_balls'][1],\n                    record['front_balls'][2],\n                    record['front_balls'][3],\n                    record['front_balls'][4],\n                    record['back_balls'][0],\n                    record['back_balls'][1],\n                    record['pool_amount'],\n                    record['sales_amount'],\n                    record['issue_number']\n                ))\n                updated += 1\n            else:\n                # 插入新记录\n                cursor.execute('''\n                    INSERT INTO lottery_records (\n                        issue_number, draw_date,\n                        front_ball_1, front_ball_2, front_ball_3,\n                        front_ball_4, front_ball_5,\n                        back_ball_1, back_ball_2,\n                        pool_amount, sales_amount\n                    ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\n                ''', (\n                    record['issue_number'],\n                    record['draw_date'],\n                    record['front_balls'][0],\n                    record['front_balls'][1],\n                    record['front_balls'][2],\n                    record['front_balls'][3],\n                    record['front_balls'][4],\n                    record['back_balls'][0],\n                    record['back_balls'][1],\n                    record['pool_amount'],\n                    record['sales_amount']\n                ))\n                inserted += 1\n                \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"⚠️ 保存记录失败 {record['issue_number']}: {e}\")\n            continue\n    \n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n    \n    print(f\"✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 {inserted} 条, 更新 {updated} 条\")\n    return inserted + updated\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 检查数据库是否存在\n    if not DB_PATH.exists():\n        print(\"⚠️ 数据库未初始化，正在初始化...\")\n        import init_db\n        init_db.init_database()\n    \n    fetch_all_history()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778750665791}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f61d696","parentId":"8b177577","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:24:34.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户询问能否获取历史全部开奖数据。从 fetch_history.py 的代码来看，这个脚本目前只抓取彩票500万网站的默认页面数据（没有分页逻辑），所以只能获取到默认显示的30条左右记录。\n\n彩票500万网站应该有分页或者可以加载更多历史数据的参数。我需要：\n1. 检查网站是否有分页或分页参数\n2. 修改脚本来支持分页抓取\n3. 循环抓取所有历史数据\n\n让我先运行一下脚本看看实际能抓取多少条数据，然后考虑是否需要修改脚本支持分页。\n\n从代码来看，BASE_URL = \"https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\"，这个URL可能需要参数来获取不同页的数据。\n\n让我先尝试访问这个页面，看看是否有分页参数或者其他方式获取全部历史数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-387bb2609a3049f684f705e327f3bdc5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\" | grep -o \"总记录数.*\" | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1839,"output":226,"cacheRead":50304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52369,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778750665794,"responseId":"20260514172426a1ce85a7b79f40ca","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
