{"type":"message","id":"5b2331bd","parentId":"96589072","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:24:46.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n看来彩票500万网站有了防护机制（567错误，EdgeOne防护），直接用curl访问会被拦截。但刚才的Python脚本成功抓取了数据，说明脚本使用了User-Agent等header可以正常访问。\n\n从脚本代码来看，它只访问了一次BASE_URL，没有分页逻辑。这说明彩票500万这个页面默认显示最近30条数据。\n\n要获取全部历史数据，我需要：\n1. 检查网站是否有分页参数或API\n2. 或者检查是否有其他方式获取更多历史数据\n\n让我看看大乐透技能的目录结构，是否有其他相关的脚本或文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d9f2757413ac493a88d518e9e0ae6066","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && ls -la"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2655,"output":154,"cacheRead":52224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778750679366,"responseId":"2026051417243959fc58972b6c4230","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
