{"type":"message","id":"0b011f57","parentId":"acef4cf9","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:28:41.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-4b14f24b8a524c45a897dbc62994e3da","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🚀 抓取全部历史数据...\n============================================================\n🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取（增强版）\n============================================================\n\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\n   URL: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php?start=05001&end=26052\n📊 正在解析数据...\n✅ 成功抓取 2870 条记录\n   📅 期号范围: 26052 ~ 07001\n✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 2836 条, 更新 34 条\n\n✅ 总计保存 2870 条记录\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:174: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:204: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2054,"aggregated":"🚀 抓取全部历史数据...\n============================================================\n🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取（增强版）\n============================================================\n\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\n   URL: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php?start=05001&end=26052\n📊 正在解析数据...\n✅ 成功抓取 2870 条记录\n   📅 期号范围: 26052 ~ 07001\n✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 2836 条, 更新 34 条\n\n✅ 总计保存 2870 条记录\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:174: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:204: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recip