{"type":"message","id":"1a695e15","parentId":"5496faff","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:29:17.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n完美！成功抓取了全部历史数据。现在给用户一个清晰的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 大乐透全量数据抓取完成 🍀\n\n### 抓取结果\n\n| 项目 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| **抓取方式** | 彩票500万网（全量） |\n| **总记录数** | **2,870 条** |\n| **新增记录** | 2,836 条 |\n| **更新记录** | 34 条 |\n| **期号范围** | 07001 ~ 26052 |\n| **历史跨度** | 19 年（2007-2026） |\n\n### 最新开奖记录\n\n| 项目 | 数据 |\n|------|------|\n| **期号** | 26052 |\n| **开奖日期** | 2026-05-13（周三） |\n| **前区** | 02 03 20 28 33 |\n| **后区** | 02 12 |\n| **完整号码** | 02 03 20 28 33 + 02 12 |\n\n### 脚本新功能\n\n现在支持多种抓取方式：\n```bash\n# 抓取全部历史数据\npython scripts/fetch_history.py --all\n\n# 指定期数范围\npython scripts/fetch_history.py --start 05001 --end 06000\n\n# 默认抓取最近30条\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n数据已全部保存到数据库：`/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/data/super_lotto.db`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":873,"output":339,"cacheRead":64128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778750948485,"responseId":"202605141729084dbe311f2274474c","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"771423d7","parentId":"1a695e15","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:34:24.140Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-14 17:34 GMT+8] 太棒了。我觉的奇怪的事情是，双色球技能更新到本地数据库中的记录上万条，历史上双色球开奖已经上万了吗？"}],"timestamp":1778751264100}}
