{"type":"message","id":"d5c09d30","parentId":"14db0362","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:35:02.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户问了个好问题：双色球数据库有上万条记录，但历史上真的有上万期开奖吗？\n\n让我计算一下：\n- 双色球每周开奖3次（周二、四、日）\n- 一年大约52周，每周3期 = 156期/年\n- 从2003年开始（双色球2003年2月16日首期），到2026年约23年\n- 23年 × 156期 = 3,588期左右\n\n所以双色球从开始到现在应该只有3000-4000期左右，不应该有上万条记录。\n\n之前我查询到的数据库总记录数是2,011条（在 fetch_history.py 的输出中），这是合理的。但用户说\"上万条\"，可能是看到了112,616这个数字（这是在双色球数据抓取时显示的\"当前已抓取\"数量，但实际保存的只有2,011条）。\n\n让我重新查询双色球数据库的实际记录数，给用户一个准确的答案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你问得很好！让我确认一下双色球数据库的实际记录数 🍀"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-6dcd353f98cf44ad917cfa709a721fd3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nimport os\n\n# 切换到双色球技能目录\nos.chdir('/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball')\n\n# 连接数据库\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/double_color_ball.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\n\n# 查询总记录数\ncursor.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM lottery_records')\ntotal = cursor.fetchone()[0]\n\n# 查询最早和最晚期号\ncursor.execute('SELECT MIN(issue_number), MAX(issue_number) FROM lottery_records')\nmin_issue, max_issue = cursor.fetchone()\n\n# 查询最早和最晚日期\ncursor.execute('SELECT MIN(draw_date), MAX(draw_date) FROM lottery_records')\nmin_date, max_date = cursor.fetchone()\n\n# 查询最新3期\ncursor.execute('''\n    SELECT issue_number, draw_date\n    FROM lottery_records\n    ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    LIMIT 3\n''')\nlatest_3 = cursor.fetchall()\n\nprint(f'📊 数据库总记录数: {total:,}')\nprint(f'📅 期号范围: {min_issue} ~ {max_issue}')\nprint(f'📆 日期范围: {min_date} ~ {max_date}')\nprint(f'\\n📋 最新3期开奖:')\nfor issue, date in latest_3:\n    print(f'   期号 {issue}: {date}')\n\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":65389,"output":534,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778751264143,"responseI