{"type":"message","id":"6b34c2b2","parentId":"b905ad7b","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:46:16.162Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n太好了！数据是存在的，而且是最早期的数据（03001-03005，2003年2-3月）。问题是脚本没有正确解析。\n\n从HTML结构看，数据确实是有的，所以可能是BeautifulSoup解析的问题，或者我需要调整解析逻辑。\n\n让我修改脚本，使用更健壮的解析方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！数据存在，是最早期的开奖记录（03001期，2003年2月23日）！\n\n问题是脚本解析失败了。让我修复解析器："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-da334e8c2f614ea88f1fba87be1b2f00","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball/scripts/fetch_history.py","edits":[{"oldText":"def parse_html(html_content):\n    \"\"\"解析HTML内容，提取开奖数据\"\"\"\n    records = []\n    soup = BeautifulSoup(html_content, 'html.parser')\n\n    # 查找所有行\n    rows = soup.find_all('tr', {'class': 't_tr1'})\n\n    for row in rows:\n        try:\n            tds = row.find_all('td')\n            if len(tds) < 12:\n                continue\n\n            # 期号\n            issue_number = tds[0].get_text(strip=True)\n\n            # 开奖日期\n            draw_date_str = tds[1].get_text(strip=True)\n            draw_date = datetime.strptime(draw_date_str, '%Y-%m-%d').date()\n\n            # 红球（6个）\n            red_balls = []\n            for i in range(2, 8):\n                ball = int(tds[i].get_text(strip=True))\n                red_balls.append(ball)\n\n            # 蓝球\n            blue_ball = int(tds[8].get_text(strip=True))\n\n            records.append({\n                'issue_number': issue_number,\n                'draw_date': draw_date,\n                'red_balls': red_balls,\n                'blue_ball': blue_ball\n            })\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            continue\n\n    return records","newText":"def parse_html(html_content):\n    \"\"\"解析HTML内容，提取开奖数据\"\"\"\n    records = []\n    soup = BeautifulSoup(html_content, 'html.parser')\n\n    # 查找所有行\n    rows = soup.find_all('tr', {'class': 't_tr1'})\n\n    for row in rows:\n        try:\n            tds = row.find_all('td')\n            if len(tds) < 15:\n                continue\n\n            # 期号（在td[1]，第一个td是序号）\n            issue_number = tds[1].get_text(strip=True)\n\n            # 红球（6个，在td[2:8]）\n            red_balls = []\n            for i in range(2, 8):\n                ball_str = tds[i].get_text(strip=True)\n                # 清理可能的特殊字符（如&nbsp;）\n                ball_str = ball_str.split()[0] if ball_str else ''\n                if ball_str.isdigit():\n                    red_balls.append(int(ball_str))\n\n            # 蓝球（在td[8]）\n            blue_str = tds[8].get_text(strip=True)\n            blue_str = blue_str.split()[0] if blue_str else ''\n            if blue_str.isdigit():\n                blue_ball = int(blue_str)\n            else:\n                continue\n\n            # 开奖日期（在最后一个td）\n            draw_date_str = tds[-1].get_text(strip=True)\n            if draw_date_str:\n                try:\n                    draw_date = datetime.strptime(draw_date_str, '%Y-%m-%d').date()\n                except:\n                    continue\n            else:\n                continue\n\n            # 验证数据完整性\n            if len(red_balls) == 6 and blue_ball:\n                records.append({\n                    'issue_number': issue_number,\n                    'draw_date': draw_date,\n                    'red_balls': red_balls,\n                    'blue_ball': blue_ball\n                })\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            # 调试输出\n            # print(f\"解析行失败: {e}\")\n            continue\n\n    return records"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1172,"output":968,"cacheRead":71424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73564,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778751956748,"responseId":"2026051417455776819379dcdc4303","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
