{"type":"message","id":"dd5c4268","parentId":"732ae9cc","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:46:33.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n嗯，只抓取了221条记录，期号范围是04-10，这不对。应该是从03001到2026053，应该有3000多条记录。\n\n问题是500彩票网可能也有类似大乐透的反爬虫机制，或者一次请求返回的数据有限制。\n\n让我测试一下不同的参数范围，看看能否一次性获取更多数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据不完整！只抓取了221条，而且期号范围异常（04-10）。\n\n让我测试一下500彩票网的参数限制："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e81e2de15a6646048383e45935398a2a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport requests\n\nHEADERS = {\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n}\n\ntest_cases = [\n    ('start=03001&end=03010', '最早10期'),\n    ('start=200501&end=200510', '2005年10期'),\n    ('start=2025001&end=2026053', '最近2年'),\n]\n\nfor params, desc in test_cases:\n    url = f'https://datachart.500.com/ssq/history/newinc/history.php?{params}'\n    resp = requests.get(url, headers=HEADERS, timeout=10)\n    count = resp.text.count('t_tr1')\n    print(f'{desc}: {count} 条')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":514,"output":320,"cacheRead":73344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778751983626,"responseId":"2026051417462397934e2faf6c466e","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
