{"type":"message","id":"d1b6ac40","parentId":"54028354","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:46:42.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n问题找到了！500彩票网的参数格式和我预期的不一样。它可能只支持很短的时间范围，或者参数格式有问题。\n\n让我尝试使用官方API（中国福利彩票网）来获取全部历史数据。之前双色球就是用cwl数据源的，被403拦截了，但我可以尝试调整参数或者使用其他方式。\n\n让我先试试官方API能否正常工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"500彩票网的参数格式有问题。让我用官方API（中国福利彩票网）尝试分页抓取："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-451a9ad839854c7aa84c567de2dc7d22","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://www.cwl.gov.cn/cwl_admin/front/cwlkj/search/kjxx/findDrawNotice?name=ssq&issueCount=5000&pageNo=1&pageSize=500\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36\" | python3 -m json.tool | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":478,"output":221,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74427,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778751994965,"responseId":"20260514174635c791fccdd3c64504","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
