{"type":"message","id":"fafbeddb","parentId":"e01a23aa","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:47:45.943Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有批次都没有数据返回，这说明500彩票网的期号格式可能是4位而不是7位。让我测试一下不同格式的期号。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"所有批次都失败了！500彩票网的期号格式可能不是7位。让我测试一下正确的格式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4b22132336764a53afba7b04","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport requests\n\nHEADERS = {\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n}\n\n# 测试不同期号格式\ntest_cases = [\n    ('start=3&end=12', '3-12期'),\n    ('start=3&end=20', '3-20期'),\n    ('start=100&end=200', '100-200期'),\n    ('start=2013&end=2026', '4位年'),\n]\n\nfor params, desc in test_cases:\n    url = f'https://datachart.500.com/ssq/history/newinc/history.php?{params}'\n    resp = requests.get(url, headers=HEADERS, timeout=10)\n    count = resp.text.count('t_tr1')\n    print(f'{desc}: {count} 条')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":774,"output":274,"cacheRead":72448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778752062728,"responseId":"20260514174743b0478a3bedf6460c","responseModel":"glm-4.7"}}
