{"type":"message","id":"859ac63a","parentId":"92b3e057","timestamp":"2026-05-14T09:49:40.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了！官方API只返回了2011条数据，这说明：\n\n1. 官方API可能只提供最近几年的数据（从2013年开始）\n2. 或者需要调整API参数才能获取更早期的数据\n\n让我查询一下数据库，看看实际的期号范围和日期范围，确认是否已经获取了全部可用的历史数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完成！让我查看最终结果 🍀"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88d335f74def440993fa1ac9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nimport os\n\nos.chdir('/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball')\n\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/double_color_ball.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\n\n# 查询总记录数\ncursor.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM lottery_records')\ntotal = cursor.fetchone()[0]\n\n# 查询最早和最晚期号\ncursor.execute('SELECT MIN(issue_number), MAX(issue_number) FROM lottery_records')\nmin_issue, max_issue = cursor.fetchone()\n\n# 查询最早和最晚日期\ncursor.execute('SELECT MIN(draw_date), MAX(draw_date) FROM lottery_records')\nmin_date, max_date = cursor.fetchone()\n\nprint(f'📊 数据库总记录数: {total:,}')\nprint(f'📅 期号范围: {min_issue} ~ {max_issue}')\nprint(f'📆 日期范围: {min_date} ~ {max_date}')\nprint(f'⏱️ 历史跨度: {(max_date.year - min_date.year)} 年')\n\n# 查询最新5期\nprint(f'\\n📋 最新5期开奖:')\ncursor.execute('''\n    SELECT issue_number, draw_date,\n           red_ball_1, red_ball_2, red_ball_3, red_ball_4, red_ball_5, red_ball_6, blue_ball\n    FROM lottery_records\n    ORDER BY issue_number DESC\n    LIMIT 5\n''')\nfor row in cursor.fetchall():\n    issue, date, *balls, blue = row\n    red_balls = sorted(balls[:6])\n    print(f'   期号 {issue}: {date} | {\" \".join([f\"{x:02d}\" for x in red_balls])} + {blue:02d}')\n\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":359,"output":469,"cacheRead":79296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778752173613,"responseId":"2026051417493